TopicTitle: Duct fan and blades fitting xbox

Articles.Content: Struggling with duct fan and current blades on xbox. Were there not duct fan blades? I swear I saw them. They don't seem to be on xbox.
Ducted fan blades are from a DLC that is available for PC. The console version of the game is not up to the same version as on the PC, and DLC content may not be available.
